column2: SELECT TOP #  S.ObjID, S.z,S.sn_#,  &&&, L2.ew ,  &&&,L3.ew FROM SpecPhoto AS S  JOIN SpecLine AS L2 ON S.SpecObjID = L2.SpecObjID  JOIN SpecLine AS L3 ON S.SpecObjID = L3.SpecObjID  JOIN SpecObjAll as sn_# ON S.SpecObjID = sn_#.SpecObjID  WHERE  L2.LineId = #  and L3.LineID = # and (S.specclass=# or S.specclass=#) and S.zconf > .# and S.z < .#
